output.control_stream:
$SIZES MAXFCN = 5000000 $PROBLEM Dual Numbers benchmark $INPUT ID TIME AMT DV WT ;; $DATA c:/git/adpoBenchmark/data/sim_1_2_1_0.csv IGNORE=@ $DATA d:/git/adpobenchmark/data/sim_1_2_1_0.csv IGNORE=@
$SUBROUTINE ADVAN6 TOL=7 $MODEL COMP=(DEPOT,DEFDOSE) COMP=(CENTRAL,NODOSE,DEFOBS) COMP=(PERI,NODOSE) $PK CWT = WT/70
TVVMAX= THETA(1) VMAX=TVVMAX*EXP(ETA(1)) TVKM = THETA(2) KM = TVKM *EXP(ETA(2)) TVV2=THETA(3) *CWT**THETA(5) V2=TVV2 *EXP(ETA(3)) TVKA=THETA(4) KA=TVKA K23=THETA(6) K32=THETA(7) SC = V2 $ERROR IPRED = F Y=F*EXP(EPS(2)) + EPS(1) $DES CONC = A(2)/SC DADT(1) = -KA*A(1) DADT(2) = KA*A(1)-VMAX*CONC/(KM+CONC) -K23*A(2)+K32*A(3) DADT(3) = K23*A(2)-K32*A(3)
$THETA (100,4000) ; THETA(1) VMAX UNITS = MG/HR (100,4000) ; THETA(2) KM UNITS = CONC (0,50) ; THETA(3) V UNITS = L (0,1.2) ; THETA(4) KA UNITS = 1/HR
(0,1.1) ;; THETA(5) V~WT (0.0001,2) ;; THETA(6) K23 (0.0001,3) ;; THETA(7) K32 ; empty $OMEGA $OMEGA 0.1 ; ETA(1) ETA ON VMAX 0.1 ; ETA(2) ETA ON KM 0.1 ; ETA(3) ETA ON V2 $SIGMA (1) ;; EPS(1) ADDITIVE (0.3) ;; EPS(2) PROPORTIONAL $EST METHOD=COND INTER MAXEVALS=9999 NOHABORT NOOMEGABOUNDTEST NOSIGMABOUNDTEST NOTHETABOUNDTEST $COV UNCOND PRECOND=2 ;;; Model Identifier = 1,2,1,0
$TABLE ID TIME IPRED DV NOAPPEND ONEHEADER NOPRINT FILE= Run1Preds.dat
;; Phenotype: ([('COMP', 1), ('ETAs', 2), ('V~WT', 1), ('GAMMA', 0)]) ;; Genotype: [1, 2, 1, 0] ;; Num non-influential tokens: 0
